high_descs: Turn around and walk to the kitchen counter with the lettuce on the counter.
Grab the spatula next to the bread loaf and toaster.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the spatula in the sink, rinse the spatula, and then grab the spatula.
Turn left and walk to the toaster.
Turn around and place the spatula to the right of the sink.
Turn around and head towards the lettuce on the counter.
Pick up the spatula on the left corner of the counter.
Turn right and head towards the sink, face the sink.
Place the spatula in the sink, wash the spatula, and pick up the spatula.
Turn left, walk a little towards the lettuce, and turn around to face the apple on the counter.
Place the spatula to the left of the knife on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Placed the clean spatula next to the knife on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to the counter top containing the spatula.
Pick up the spatula from the counter top.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the spatula in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Move slightly to the left of the sink.
Put the spatula on the counter top to the right of the sink, to the left of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned spatula on a counter top.

high_descs: Turn right and take one step, then turn right and walk across the room.
Look down to pick up the spatula.
Turn to the right and take one step, then turn to the left to face the sink.
Place the spatula on the bottom edge inside the sink, turn on the faucet for three seconds, then turn the faucet off and take the spatula.
Turn left and take one step, then turn right to face the counter.
Look to the right and and place the spatula on the right side of the sink.
Turn right and walk until you hit the counter and face it after moving yourself slightly to the left
Pick up the spatula to the top left of your field of view.
Turn right and position yourself in front of the sink facing it.
Put the spatula in the sink and run the water to get it wet and clean.
Turn left and position yourself in the same spot as before when you got the spatula.
Put the spatula back in it's place.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean spatula on the counter.
